==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A person who favors maintenance of the [[status quo]] or reversion to some earlier status.
# {{cattag|UK|politics}} A member of the [[Conservative party]].
# {{cattag|US|economics}} A [[fiscal conservative]]
# {{cattag|US|politics}} A [[political conservative]]
# {{cattag|US|social sciences}} A [[social conservative]].
# {{cattag|US|politics}} One who favors the [[Republican party]], regardless of its conservatism in other senses.

